## Data Points

**master_stock_universe.py**
* symbol
* companyName
* marketCap
* sector
* industry
* volume
* exchange
* isEtf
* isFund
* isActivelyTrading

**active_stock_universe.py**
* same as master_stock_universe.py

**large_actives_with_metrics.py**
* symbol
* company_name
* market_cap_usd
* ipo_date
* growth_risk_score: (2·growth_score + risk_score) / 3 — blank if either is blank
* growth_score: 0.35·P(sales_growth_ttm_vs_prior_ttm_pct) + 0.25·P(sales_growth_latest_q_yoy_pct) + 0.20·P(sales_growth_3yr_vs_prior_3yr_pct) + 0.10·P(gross_profit_to_sales_ttm_pct) + 0.10·P(gross_profit_to_sales_yoy_change_pp) — P(x) = percentile rank within the batch (0–100; blanks re-normalize)
* risk_score: higher = safer. 0.30·(100 − P(total_debt_to_sales_pct)) + 0.125·P(lowest-7y fcf/sales) + 0.125·(100 − P(fcf_to_sales_vs_7yr_trough_pp)) + 0.125·P(lowest-7y gross-profit/sales) + 0.125·(100 − P(gross_profit_to_sales_vs_7yr_trough_pp)) + 0.10·P(lowest-7y sales growth) + 0.10·(100 − P(sales_growth_vs_7yr_trough_pp)) — the three "lowest-7y" levels are ranking inputs, not columns
* ev_to_sales_ttm: (market_cap_usd + total debt − cash) / sales_ttm_usd (total debt & cash from the latest quarter, converted to USD)
* pe_ratio_ttm: market_cap_usd / TTM net income (converted to USD; blank if net income ≤ 0)
* analyst_buy_pct: (strongBuy + buy) / (strongBuy + buy + hold + sell + strongSell) × 100
* analyst_count: strongBuy + buy + hold + sell + strongSell
* description
* sector
* industry
* sales_ttm_usd: TTM sales (sum of the last 4 quarters), converted to USD at the spot FX rate
* sales_growth_ttm_vs_prior_ttm_pct: (TTM sales / prior-year TTM sales − 1) × 100
* sales_growth_latest_q_yoy_pct: (latest-quarter sales / the same quarter one year earlier − 1) × 100
* sales_growth_3yr_vs_prior_3yr_pct: (average of the last 3 annual sales / average of the prior 3 annual sales − 1) × 100
* gross_profit_to_sales_ttm_pct: (TTM gross profit / TTM sales) × 100
* gross_profit_to_sales_yoy_change_pp: (TTM gross-profit/sales) − (prior-year TTM gross-profit/sales), in percentage points
* fcf_to_sales_ttm_pct: (TTM free cash flow / TTM sales) × 100
* total_debt_to_sales_pct: (total debt [latest quarter] / TTM sales) × 100
* sales_growth_vs_7yr_trough_pp: sales_growth_ttm_vs_prior_ttm_pct − lowest annual sales growth of the last 7 years — blank if < 7 years of history
* gross_profit_to_sales_vs_7yr_trough_pp: gross_profit_to_sales_ttm_pct − lowest annual gross-profit/sales of the last 7 years — blank if < 7 years
* fcf_to_sales_vs_7yr_trough_pp: fcf_to_sales_ttm_pct − lowest annual FCF/sales of the last 7 years — blank if < 7 years
* shares_outstanding_yoy_change_pct: (latest annual diluted weighted-average shares / prior year − 1) × 100 (positive = dilution, negative = buyback)
* exchange
* volume

